node.text: Pete Buttigieg and his husband Chasten Buttigieg just added two new additions to their family. 🙏 After revealing their fatherhood news last month, the U.S. secretary of transportation posted their first family photo with each parent holding one of the twins, a boy and a girl. "Chasten and I are beyond thankful for all the kind wishes since first sharing the news that we're becoming parents," they wrote in a joint statement. "We are delighted to welcome Penelope Rose and Joseph August Buttigieg to our family." Tap the link in bio for more! #Regram @pete.buttigieg
